    {
      "id": "f50984f1-93db-4b61-8ff5-cb0e5dd942f8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Data used encompasses student carachteristics, Moodle interactions and grades. Results highlight that the main contributors to performance are: Access, Questionnaire, Task and Age. Clustering results also show that interactions are correlated with performance. ",
